values: All posts now have a security level of at least friends-only. This means, if you want to view my posts, you have to be added. This is, among other things, a sexual venting grounds. It's quite explicit. If the kinds of things listed on my interests in my profile offend you, don't request to be added. If you would like to be added, comment on this post. Your birthdate must be visible on your profile, you must tell me why you wish to be added, and how you found me or my journal. If you can do these things, you can probably be added.
